MC is a Health Department programme. It: MC ke lenaneo la Lefapha la Boitekanelo. Le romela diSMS tsa gago & lesea. Go bona, fetola kgotsa go phimola dintlha tsa gago leletsa *134*550*7#
MomConnect needs your personal info to s: MomConnect e tlhoka dintlha tsa gago go go romelela melaetsa e e siametseng maemo a boimana ba gago kgotsa bogolo ba lesea. Ka go itse gore o kwadiseditse MomConnect kae, Lefapha la Boitekanelo le ka dira gore tirelo e rebolelwe basadi kwa tliliniking ya gago. Go itse kwa o kwadisitseng teng go tla thusa Lefapha la Boitekanelo go tsaya tsia ditshwaelo tse o di romelang MomConnect ka maitemogelo a gago.
MomConnect collects your phone and ID nu: MomConnect e tsaya dinomoro tsa gago tsa mogala le ID, tliliniki le dintlha tsa boimana ba gago.
MomConnect is owned and run by the Healt: MomConnect ke ya Lefapha la Boitekanelo. MTN, Cell C, Telkom, Praekelt, Jembi le HISP di kokoanya le go dirisa dintlha tsa gago boemong ba lona.
You can see, change, or ask us to delete: O ka bona, fetola kgotsa wa re kopa go phimola dintlha tsa gago ka go leletsa *134*550*7#
MomConnect will automatically delete you: MomConnect e tla phimola dintlha tsa gago dingwaga tse 7 le dikgwedi tse 9 morago ga gore o ikwadise.
